Package: arronax
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.4), ${python3:Depends}, gir1.2-glib-2.0,  gir1.2-gtk-3.0, python3-gi (>= 2.90), gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0, python3-pkg-resources, libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.18)
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
 (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the standalone version of Arronax. 


Package: arronax-base
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, arronax 
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
 (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This is a metapackage that depends on the standalone version of
 Arronax. It doesn't contain any important files and may be removed
 without doing any harm.

Package: arronax-nautilus
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, arronax, python-nautilus
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
 (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the Nautilus plugin for Arronax. It adds a 
 "Create starter" menu item to the Desktop's context menu and to the file 
 context menu in Nautilus


Package: arronax-caja
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, arronax, python-caja
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
 (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the Caja plugin for Arronax. It adds a 
 "Create starter" menu item to the Desktop's context menu and to the file 
 context menu in Caja


Package: arronax-nemo
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, arronax, python-nemo|nemo-python
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
 Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
 (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
 .
 This package contains the Nemo plugin for Arronax. It adds a 
 "Create starter" menu item to the Desktop's context menu and to the file 
 context menu in Nemo
 
